{
  "message": "bd-s7aq: add FP-P2D-038 merge_sort parity coverage for index/alias key paths\n\nAdd dedicated packet coverage for merge sort behavior across index-driven and\naliased-key merge execution paths so sort semantics are validated beyond direct\ncolumn-key merges.\n\nWhat was added:\n- New packet fixtures under `FP-P2D-038`:\n  - `dataframe_merge_index_sort_true_inner_strict`\n  - `dataframe_merge_index_sort_false_inner_hardened`\n  - `dataframe_merge_left_index_right_on_sort_true_strict`\n  - `dataframe_merge_left_on_right_index_sort_true_hardened`\n- New packet gate artifact:\n  - `artifacts/phase2c/FP-P2D-038/parity_gate.yaml`\n- New packet filter test:\n  - `packet_filter_runs_dataframe_merge_sort_index_alias_packet`\n\nCoverage intent:\n- Validate `merge_sort` true/false behavior when joining via:\n  - index-index (`dataframe_merge_index`)\n  - left index vs right column (`left_index + right_on_keys`)\n  - left column vs right index (`left_on_keys + right_index`)\n- Confirm sorted key ordering and expected stable output contracts in both\n  strict and hardened modes.\n\nValidation performed:\n- `rch exec -- cargo fmt`\n- `rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/tmp/rch_target_redraven cargo test -p fp-conformance packet_filter_runs_dataframe_merge_sort_index_alias_packet -- --nocapture`\n- `rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/tmp/rch_target_redraven cargo run -p fp-conformance --bin fp-conformance-cli -- --packet-id FP-P2D-038 --oracle fixture --require-green`\n- `rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/tmp/rch_target_redraven cargo run -p fp-conformance --bin fp-conformance-cli -- --packet-id FP-P2D-038 --oracle live --allow-system-pandas-fallback --require-green`\n- `rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/tmp/rch_target_redraven cargo check --workspace --all-targets`\n- `rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/tmp/rch_target_redraven cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings`\n- `rch exec -- cargo fmt --check`\n- `UBS_MAX_DIR_SIZE_MB=0 ubs --staged .` (baseline pre-existing warnings)",
